sentence\": \"She sported a casual white-and-navy shirt with a delicate silver choker necklace, also opting to wear her side-parted hair down and straight.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was her husband's look that caught our eye.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"William, for his part, opted for an official Team GB Olympics polo from Adidas and showed off a scruffy beard, marking one of the first times that he had not been fresh-faced in public.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7387694329769967e-15, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well done on all you have achieved.\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have been an inspiration to us all,\\\" William, 42, added in the video.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"William and Kate did not travel to Paris for the 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9999971755218082, \"rank\": 2.824258394507929e-06, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999837068573, \"rank\": 1.6293212548890284e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Princess of Wales has recently been recuperating from chemotherapy treatment.\", \"from